:"b6eb65e2a002daa907c0baa02ffc11d781f27535","tid":934352,"uid":269686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064d24f1dcdbed23f0e0b0e98fa70bb8033c9a2a","tid":934352,"uid":97258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:52:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"101fe9230bcf3edfb5671bb22ee93a719413b6b5","tid":934352,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:39:42.000Z","msg":"英國重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n記得同父母講簽左有咩好處<br />\n點解要簽?<br />\n1.居英權 <br />\n2.去美國唔洗簽證 <br />\n3.英國係法治，非人治 <br />\n4.民主自由 <br />\n5.房屋政策教好 <br />\n6. 去歐美國家入境時唔會被問長問短 <br />\n7. 00後可以用家庭團聚形式入籍 <br />\n8.攞到脫離現有被強加國籍啲條件<br />\n9.英國無再教育營<br />\n10.無2047問題<br />\n11.因為多左英國公民喺香港，英國政府會易D發聲<br />\n12.如取消左被強加國籍，可以喺香港call領事保護及用英國護照入境中國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPostal code 填000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=%2FCoEWZ1oSvMNVxao%2BLpiVjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=c62e86bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"46f841d25c5587f73ec443e6600f7f10b0de3569","tid":934352,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80223907bcb6d5e0bc3ad4cc134d9a619dcfca7","tid":934352,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T19:02:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0edb